latestPosts.caption:
Kunika ♥️
#bridesofHarleenVirdi

From my very first conversation with Kunika about her bridal look, she told me she wanted to feel like the most natural version of herself. I knew I had to create that soft, minimalistic glow—just enough to enhance her beauty while staying true to her style. For the hair, we chose to leave it down—effortless yet elegant—perfectly completing her modern-day bridal look in the most timeless way.
